title: American Horror Story : sister eunice tells lanna she's pregnant 2x9
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: lily rabe is amazing. she have two mannerisms for each character. mary eunice before and after, the way they talk and walk totally different.

I think AHS is still a great show, and no season has been "bad", they're just all very different. And Sarah Paulson is freaking amazing. 

But god I miss Jessica Lange.
Funny how Lana Winters will probably never know that she not only was in a room by herself but holding a full on conversation (Including sass) With satan himself and lived unscathed!
I don’t get why Sister Mary Eunice was kinda cast aside in the plot. You’d think the Devil would play more of a major role and last at least until the last episode.
